[thinking] I’m considering that the behavior I've noted is indeed supported, especially regarding the scanner category being generic. According to the documentation, it's clear that generic classes should be annotated with `@ContextConfiguration`. This makes me wonder if there's anything more specific to explore regarding how these annotations interact with the scanner and whether there are any nuances I should keep in mind. It's important to ensure that everything is in line with those guidelines!
